#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "1. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Sāriputtasutta"
msgstr "3. Sāriputta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā "
"sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Sāriputta went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said "
"to him:"

msgctxt "sn45.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sakalamidaṃ, bhante, brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā "
"kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, good friends, companions, and associates are the whole of the "
"spiritual life.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.3:2.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "sn45.3:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sakalamidaṃ, sāriputta, brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā "
"kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā."
msgstr ""
"Good friends, companions, and associates are the whole of the spiritual life."

msgctxt "sn45.3:2.3"
msgid ""
"Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ kalyāṇasahāyassa "
"kalyāṇasampavaṅkassa—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with good friends, companions, and associates can expect to "
"develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn45.3:2.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, sāriputta, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.3:3.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, sāriputta, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.3:3.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, sāriputta, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.3:4.1"
msgid ""
"Tadamināpetaṃ, sāriputta, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sakalamidaṃ "
"brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā."
msgstr ""
"And here’s another way to understand how good friends are the whole of the "
"spiritual life."

msgctxt "sn45.3:4.2"
msgid ""
"Mamañhi, sāriputta, kalyāṇamittaṃ āgamma jātidhammā sattā jātiyā "
"parimuccanti; jarādhammā sattā jarāya parimuccanti; maraṇadhammā sattā "
"maraṇena parimuccanti; sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā sattā "
"sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsehi parimuccanti."
msgstr ""
"For, by relying on me as a good friend, sentient beings who are liable to "
"rebirth, old age, and death, to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and "
"distress are freed from all these things."

msgctxt "sn45.3:4.3"
msgid ""
"Iminā kho etaṃ, sāriputta, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sakalamidaṃ "
"brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is another way to understand how good friends are the whole of the "
"spiritual life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.3:4.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
